Japanese stocks firmer in London in thin trade . Japanese stocks were slightly firmer in London in thin and featureless trading . " The market is up on the back of the FTSE ( reaching new record highs ) and Wall Street has a firmer bias , but there ' s no volume , " said one dealer . By 1335 GMT , the Nikkei 50 average was up 2 . 85 points in London to 1 , 418 . 90 . In Tokyo , the benchmark Nikkei 225 average rose 20 . 60 points to 21 , 127 . 01 . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 4027 
